I even still have my school lunch box adorned with Apollo imagery. #50thAnniversary pic.twitter.com/t3UuS5MwyL

My bill supporting rural small businesses passed the House with overwhelming support. It will allow entrepreneurs in rural communities to receive the same assistance available to many other small businesses across #TN6. Read my full statement here: https://johnrose.house.gov/media/press-releases/rose-s-rural-small-business-bill-passes-house …

I was proud to sign on as a Co-Lead for the "SONG Act" this week with @RepCohen, @repjimcooper, @RepTimBurchett, and @RepDavidKustoff. This bill allows the FAA to keep those attending Tennessee’s world-class concerts and shows safe just as they do attendees of athletic events. pic.twitter.com/Y5glhyvphK
